thread.title: Samsung Galaxy Book is apparently a thing according to a new app
thread.title_full: Samsung Galaxy Book is apparently a thing according to a new app

author: Richard Devine
title: Samsung Galaxy Book is apparently a thing according to a new app
text:
Is Samsung's next Windows 10 product going to be a Surface Book-alike?
If a new app that's surfaced in the Windows Store is to be believed (h/t to the folks at MSPU ), the Samsung Galaxy Book will be the successor to the TabPro S from 2016.
